\[\|\mathbf{a} - \mathbf{b}\|^2 + \|\mathbf{a} - \mathbf{c}\|^2 + \|\mathbf{b} - \mathbf{c}\|^2 = 6 - 2 (\mathbf{a} \cdot \mathbf{b} + \mathbf{a} \cdot \mathbf{c} + \mathbf{b} \cdot \mathbf{c}).\]Now,
\[\|\mathbf{a} + \mathbf{b} + \mathbf{c}\|^2 \ge 0.\]We can expand this as
